  given edge-test-3вҶ’result вүЎ "ValueError"
  given edge-test-3вҶ’verdict вүЎ "pass"
  given edge-test-3вҶ’deeper-edges вүЎ [2024-04-31, 2024-00-15]
  given edge-test-4вҶ’result вүЎ "ambiguous вҖ” partial date"
  given edge-test-4вҶ’verdict вүЎ "ambiguous"
