  given edge-test-5вҶ’verdict вүЎ "ambiguous"
  given edge-test-5вҶ’deeper-edges вүЎ [last Wednesday, in 3 days, next Tuesday at 11pm]
  given edge-test-6вҶ’result вүЎ "ambiguous вҖ” century pivot"
  given edge-test-6вҶ’verdict вүЎ "ambiguous"
  given edge-test-6вҶ’deeper-edges вүЎ [03/15/99, 03/15/00]
  given edge-test-7вҶ’result вүЎ "ValueError"
