-- LLM evaluation:
-- Total tests: 7 (initial) + 8 (edge) = 15
-- Verdicts: 10 pass, 0 fail, 5 ambiguous
-- Deeper edges discovered but NOT YET TESTED: 16 items across 8 edge tests
