  ]
  yield total-tests вүЎ 15
  yield ambiguities вүЎ [
    "Format disambiguation: US vs European for ambiguous MM/DD inputs",
    "Partial date handling: ValueError vs default values for incomplete dates",
    "Relative date anchoring: no reference date parameter вҶ’ non-deterministic",
    "Two-digit year pivot: no specified century cutoff rule",
    "Timezone date extraction: local date vs UTC date when they differ"
  ]

-- oracle checks:
