вҠў final-test-suite
  given generate-initial-testsвҶ’test-cases вүЎ [7 initial test cases]
  given edge-test-*вҶ’result вүЎ [15 edge test results]
  given edge-test-*вҶ’verdict вүЎ [15 edge test verdicts]
